Like Ninjas? Zombies? Wolverine? Want to see Wolverine fight ninjas and zombies? THEN THIS IS THE BOOK FOR YOU! And what does the mysterious Mark of Mana have to do with it?

Collects Wolverine: Soultaker #1-5.
